metadata.name: In the Forest
metadata.description:
The last pillar of humanity resides in the eternal remembrance; the last pillar of every man tries to survive in the life force of a lotus flower.

No man can choose both: that the lotus flower may confuse the minds of mankind; or that the rock carves the stories of that man in history.

There is no truth: the Forest God welcomes all souls, regardless of the choice made.
